title: Tachku - more benefits than taxi
description:
Tachku! Your ride - at your price!
Need a taxi? Try "Tachku!" - this is a convenient app for trips around Ukraine.
Download the app and get the opportunity to set your own price for a ride!
It's simple - order a car in the app, specify the route and set your price for the ride. "Tachku!" will find the nearest free car and the driver will contact you. ETA from 3 minutes!
And if you have a car, you can earn at any time. Just install "Tachku!" and start earning right now.
Benefits:
Flexible search for a car based on your wishes (baby seat, minibus, cargo taxi, etc.)
The ability to quickly order the nearest taxi from the city map.
Detailed information about each driver (photo, name, age, as well as brand, color and plate number of the car).
Selection of the driver by rating, ratings and reviews from previous customers.
Tracking an ordered car on a city map in real time.
Saving the order history. Possibility of repeat order.
Save time and money for a taxi along with the "Tachku!". Have a good ride!
